{"tid":744161,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國強勢成為新任世界冠軍，未來4年有邊隊阻到佢地？","createTime":"2018-07-15T18:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T00:01:13.000Z","uid":44638,"like":76,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"49a2152c2892c90ffd5bf699c891c8a24c56d660","tid":744161,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:30:54.000Z","msg":"法國今屆可以講係愈踢愈好<br />\n<br />\n分組賽一般，１６強都係有點鬆散，８強開始上力穩陣，４強都嬴得合理，決賽就技壓。<br />\n<br />\n可以睇到隊波年紀係輕，但心理質素係不斷提升緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今屆已經係身價最高既國家隊，正選、後備，青訓後生仔一堆妖人仲等緊上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家迪甘斯帶既呢隊法國已經袋左一個歐國盃亞軍，世界盃冠軍<br />\n<br />\n平均年齡咁輕既班底，預計2020歐國應該係繼續係強勢。。<br />\n<br />\n甚至有力挑戰西班牙2008-2012既國際賽皇朝 <br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打點睇2年後歐國盃既法國，甚至下一屆世盃？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南美隊幾時先返返黎　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2220526a6a3d3fc8893aa9fcec456a5d7cdd198","tid":744161,"uid":34293,"like":83,"dislike":8,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:32:33.000Z","msg":"ching  出黎搞笑?"},{"pid":"65e6e3cae16fd1a4063f778e189048f286cab761","tid":744161,"uid":31744,"like":89,"dislike":10,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"唔要連加特嘅英格蘭有力一戰"},{"pid":"aec01ef27dc9f55e873b186aa317e7258c2b83ac","tid":744161,"uid":35931,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:32:48.000Z","msg":"2020歐國盃睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比利時仲有小小機架<br />\n但再下屆世界盃就真係個個變哂老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0937bc093715a69d99f5e6cbc2253ce78b3714","tid":744161,"uid":179547,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得16強同8強打得最好喎，16強雖然輸三粒，但反擊好快好準又有效率"},{"pid":"b3ae2da82505f44908d041c21fd001ed817244c5","tid":744161,"uid":3897,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18: